super_attack.name: Power Pole Dance
super_attack.effect: Greatly raises ATK & DEF for 3 turns; Causes immense damage to enemy; Raises allies' ATK by 41% for 2 turns (self excluded)

passive_skill.name: Serious Fight in the Demon Realm
